sourcesContent: import SongCard from "./../components/SongCard" let alphabet = [ "#", "A", "B", "C", "D", "E", "F", "G", "H", "I", "J", "K", "L", "M", "N", "Ñ", "O", "P", "Q", "R", "S", "T", "U", "V", "W", "X", "Y", "Z" ] export function drawSongsSection(songs) { return alphabet.map((letter) => { let songsFilteredByLetter = songs.filter((song) => song.name[0] === letter) if (songsFilteredByLetter.length) { } }) } function processSongSection(songs, title) { songs.map() } export function drawAlphabet() { return alphabet.map((letter) => {letter}) }
